  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>The Inventory Detail screen can be used to manage and update inventory attributes. Each inventory item has individual records that can be updated. By multi-selecting line items of the same inventory item, you can make bulk changes to attributes such as Inventory Status, Condition, Current Location, Supplier, Price, Cost, and Carrier. All modifications are tracked and visible in the Change Log, ensuring transparency and easy reference.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Time-Saving </strong>- Quickly update multiple records of the same inventory item at once, reducing the time spent on individual adjustments.</p></li><li><p><strong>Enhanced Control</strong> - Manage inventory attributes more effectively, from status and condition to supplier and location, all in one place.</p></li><li><p><strong>Consistency</strong> - Ensure uniform changes across similar inventory records, maintaining consistency in your inventory management.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"InventoryManagement:ManualInventoryAttributeChanges-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932787743/Inventory+Management+Resources\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932787743\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Inventory Management Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932525994\" rel=\"nofollow\">Adding Inventory Into RepairQ</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932492924/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"InventoryManagement:ManualInventoryAttributeChanges-MakingBulkChangestoInventory\">Making Bulk Changes to Inventory</h2><p /><p>On the Navigation Bar, go to <strong>Inventory</strong> \u2192 <strong>Inventory Detail</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"564\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932492924/Bulk%201.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>On the Inventory Detail screen, use the <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932525644/List+Filters\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932525644\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">filters</a> near the top of the page to locate the inventory items you would like to update.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932492924/Bulk%202.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>From the list of inventory items, click the\u00a0checkbox next to the item(s)\u00a0you would like to update. Then click the\u00a0<strong>Selected Options button</strong>\u00a0near the top right of the page.  From the list of available options, click <strong>Edit Selected</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932492924/Bulk%203.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"204\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932492924/Bulk%204.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>A Bulk Edit pop-up window will appear. Click the <strong>Attribute dropdown</strong> and select which detail you would like to change: <strong>Status</strong>, <strong>Condition</strong>, <strong>Location</strong>, <strong>Supplier</strong>, <strong>Cost</strong>, <strong>Price</strong>, <strong>Note</strong>, or <strong>Carrier</strong>. Update the new value for the field and add any notes regarding the change. When you are satisfied with your changes, click <strong>Apply</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"380\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932492924/Bulk%205.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"380\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932492924/Bulk%206.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>The inventory items will be updated to reflect the changes.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932492924/Bulk%208.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><h2 id=\"InventoryManagement:ManualInventoryAttributeChanges-BulkEditChangeLog\">Bulk Edit Change Log</h2><p>Updates from a Bulk Edit will also be visible in the Change Log when viewing inventory item details.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932492924/Bulk%2010.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.21.X</p>",
